description:
Learn how to make Thai cupcake .You can cooking it yourself at home . It is easy to do step by step . Let's do it with fun together.

What do you get from this course?

  • Through process.
  • Can be mutual activities between members of family or friends.
  • Appropriate to be snacks, or party, or even selling.
  • The ingredients, and equipments are not complicated.
  • You can create new patterns style on the cake.
title: Thai Steamed Cupcakes or Cotton-Wool Cake
